{"tid":2351237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日企社長在中國網購熒幕   到貨竟是印上熒幕圖案的鐵板","createTime":"2021-01-03T05:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T05:26:25.000Z","uid":50386,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6c4f38d284d40bd55f2e86041790abaedacdb1","tid":2351237,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"相信不少人都會透過網購平台購物，然而，網購雖然方便，且容易以較便宜的價格入手產品，但因為沒有實物可供參考，「中伏」機率還是不小。而日本明和電機社長土佐信道，最近就在在網上分享自己於中國網店網購熒幕「中伏」的經歷。<br />\n <br />\n日本日本的新銳設計及表演團體明和電機，以推出自製的另類的惡搞樂器見稱。而其社長土佐信道近日在 Twitter 上分享，指自己最近在中國購物網站 Wish 上看見一款價值 2500 日元（約港幣 HKD$186）的 10.1 吋熒幕，覺得相當划算，於是入手了 5 個。然而，到貨開箱後卻發現，該「熒幕」原來是印上熒幕圖案的「鐵板」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7F02WTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7F02WTv.png&h=8136cd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，土佐信道最後在該款鐵板加上由幾個明和電機推出的磁石貼，並在其官網以 2600 日元的價格轉售，不出數小時已全數售罄。他最後更在 Twitter 上指，自己成功賺取 500 日元差價，相當符合其公司搞笑詼諧的風格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/maywadenki/status/1341671742230515715?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmaywadenki%2Fstatus%2F1341671742230515715%3Fs%3D21&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0F6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=76c0e851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmaywadenki%2Fstatus%2F1341671742230515715%3Fs%3D21&h=67912c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/maywadenki/status/1341671742230515715?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d45db085944f9f046b8dda1835b79db6f1b820","tid":2351237,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">某蟈既 5 星<br />\n代表<br />\n偷 呃 拐 騙 搶  <br />\n5 個核心價值</span></strong>"},{"pid":"22b602a80ae7193e154d0a006f41558bbc5ee8ed","tid":2351237,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49d45db085944f9f046b8dda1835b79db6f1b820","tid":2351237,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">某蟈既 5 星<br />\n代表<br />\n偷 呃 拐 騙 搶  <br />\n5 個核心價值</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真理"}]}